Sahara ikora ku bice byinshi bya [[Aligeriya|Alijeriya]], [[Cade|Tchad]], Misiri, [[Libiya]], [[Mali]], [[Moritaniya|Mauritania]], [[Maroke|Maroc]], [[Nigeri|Niger]], Sahara y'Uburengerazuba, [[Sudani]] na [[Tunisiya|Tuniziya]] . ingana na miliyoni 9 za kilometero kare (3.500.000 sq mi), bingana na 31% bya Afurika. Turamutse tubariyemo uturere twose dufite imvura igereranije yumwaka uri munsi ya 250&nbsp;mm, Sahara yaba kilometero kare miliyoni 11 (4.200.000) sq mi) . Nimwe muntara eshatu zitandukanye zifite Fiziyogarafi nini muri Africa  .

Sahara ahanini ni amabuye ya hamada ( amabuye ashashe ); ergs (umucanga w'inyanja- uduce tunini dutwikiriwe n'musenyi ) ariko igice kinini gifite  umusenyi ufite metero zirenga 180 mu bujyejuru (590 ft) muremure.  Umuyaga cyangwa imvura y'imbonekarimwe  nibyo bikora ibiranga ubutayu:umusenyi w'ubutayu, umusenyi wo mu mirima, umusenyi w' inyanja, ikibaya cyamabuye, ibibaya bya ''kaburimbo'' ( ''reg'' ), ibibaya byumye ( ''wadi'' ), ibiyaga byumye ( ''oued'' ), hamwe nubutaka bwumunyu ( ''shati'' cyangwa ''chott'' ).  Imiterere idasanzwe igize ubutayu irimo Imiterere ya Richat muri Mauritania.

Imisozi myinshi yitandukanije cyane, ibirunga byinshi, bizamuka biva mu butayu, harimo imisozi ya Aïr, imisozi ya Ahaggar, Atlas ya Sahara, imisozi ya Tibesti, Adrar des Iforas, n’imisozi y'inyanja itukura . Impinga ndende muri Sahara ni Emi Koussi, akaba ari  ikirunga cyikingira mu gace ka Tibesti gaherereye mu majyaruguru ya Tchad.

Sahara yo hagati  irumye cyane , ikagira ibimera bike. Amajyaruguru n’amajyepfo by'ubwo butayu, hamwe n’imisozi miremire, bifite uduce tw’ibyatsi bito n’ibihuru byo mu butayu, hamwe n’ibiti n’ibihuru birebire byo muri wadis, aho ubuhehere bwikusanyiriza. Mu karere ko hagati, kakandi kumye cyane, hari uduce twinshi two mu butayu bunini: Tanezrouft, Ténéré, Ubutayu bwa Libiya, Ubutayu bw'Iburasirazuba, Ubutayu bwa Nubiya n'ibindi. Utu turere twumutse cyane akenshi nta mvura igwa.

Mu majyaruguru, Sahara yambukiranya inyanja ya Mediterane muri Egiputa ndetse nibice bya Libiya, ariko muri Cyrenaica na Maghreb, Sahara ihana imbibi n’ishyamba rya Mediterane, ishyamba ry’ibiti, hamwe n'akarere k’ibidukikije ko mu majyaruguru ya Afurika kagizwe n'ibihuru, byose bikaba bifite ikirere cya Mediterane kirangwa nimpeshyi ishyushye n'itumba rikonje kandi riragwa nimvura. ugendeye ku mahame  yibimera ya Frank White  n'impuguke mubumenyi bw'isiRobert Capot-Rey,   umupaka wamajyaruguru ya Sahara uhwanye n'umupaka wamajyaruguru w' itariki bahingiraho imikindo numupaka wamajyepfo ya esparto zitandukanye, ibyatsi bisanzwe biranga ikirere cya Mediterane igice cya Maghreb na Iberia . Imipaka yo mu majyaruguru nayo ihuye na milimetero100 (3.9 in) isohyet yimvura yumwaka. 

Mu majyepfo, Sahara ihana imbibi na Sahel, umukandara wumukenke wumye ugizwe n'uturere dufite impeshyi irimo imvura ikwira muri Afurika kuva iburasirazuba kugeza iburengerazuba. Umupaka wo mu majyepfo ya Sahara werekanwa mu bimera n'umupaka wo mu majyepfo ya ''Cornulaca monacantha'' (umunyamuryango wihanganira amapfa muri Chenopodiaceae ), cyangwa umupaka wa ruguru wa ''Cenchrus biflorus'', ibyatsi bisanzwe bya Sahel.   Ukurikije ikirere, imipaka y’amajyepfo ya Sahara ihwanye na milimetero150 (5.9 in) isohyet yimvura yumwaka (iyi ni impuzandengo yigihe kirekire, kubera ko imvura ihinduka buri mwaka). 

Imijyi y'ingenzi iherereye muri Sahara harimo Nouakchott, umurwa mukuru wa Moritaniya; Tamanrasset, Ouargla, Béchar, Hassi Messaoud, Ghardaïa, na El Oued muri Alijeriya; Timbuktu muri Mali; Agadez muri Niger; Ghat muri Libiya; na Faya-Largeau muri Tchad.

== Ikirere ==
Sahara nubutayu bunini cyane ku isi. Iherereye mu burebure bugendwamo namafarasi munsi yumusozi wa subtropical, umukandara wingenzi wa kimwe cya kabiri gihoraho cya subtropical ishyushye  yumuvuduko mwinshi aho umwuka uva muri troposse yo hejuru ubusanzwe umanuka, ushyushya ukanakamya troposufer yo hepfo ukanarinda ibicu. 
